Defining a dashboard layout { #webapi_dasboard_layout } 

You can define and save a layout for each dashboard. The following object is responsible to hold this setting.

    {
      "layout": {
        "spacing": {
          "column": 5,
          "row": 5
        },
        "columns": [{
          "index": 0,
          "span": 2
        }, {
          "index": 1,
          "span": 1
        }]
      }
    }



